{
  "stem": "14168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people that I met, I-- I got together with every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got together on Shabbat, too, on other-- on-- on-- on festive occasions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I also, at the same time, must admit that, after a year and a half, I decided that I was not cut out to become a rabbi, because my-- my view of Judaism is not necessarily the traditional way.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I decided, I-- while I have remained a Jew in-- with all my life, with all my heart-- I decided I'm not going to become a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to study other subjects.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, at the same time, I had the distinction of becoming one of the two Jewish students admitted to the University of Breslau under the numerus clausus, which is that we had a quota of two out of 20,000.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there I came in touch with a-- professors and-- who were also outstanding in the-- in philosophy, economics.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I studied, particularly, the romance languages, philology.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I must say that I have-- I encountered very, very little discrimination at the University at that time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Why that was, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Although we had one professor who taught in Nazi uniform with a swastika.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was-- that was an honor, you know, at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- they were very, very interesting people that I met and experiences.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember one seminar that I took in-- was it philosophy?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was one guy who stood up and said he was a student of Protestant theology.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said to the professor, and to the Nazis who were there, I cannot go along with the race-- racist theory.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is completely counter to what I was taught as a Christian.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we walked home.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
